<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>周六早上，美罗城阳光灿烂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探正在上班的路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他快要到达警察总局的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看到一道黑影遮住了整个广场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探抬头一看。“那是什么？”他叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个高大的银色机器人向天空喷了一道奇怪的雾气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雾气形成了一个蓝色泡泡，把警察总局包围了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“车来了！”玛拉向朋友们叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>车开进了停车场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉向司机挥手，指向一个牌子，上面写着“洗车”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好。”司机问，“洗车多少钱？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“十美元。” 玛拉说，“我们足球队正在筹钱买新队服。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔和杰克提着一桶肥皂水跑来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西拿来了一些海绵。大家开始擦车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们今天才洗了第三辆车。”特勒尔皱着眉头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。”杰克说，“我希望能来更多的车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>要不然我们买队服的钱不够。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的旧队服太丑了。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西把海绵泡进水里，在车盖上涂上泡沫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快车盖就在阳光下闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔似乎在思考什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许火箭女孩儿能帮我们弄到新队服。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们应该问问她。”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这太可笑了。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿不能帮我们弄到新队服。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么不能？”特勒尔问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为......”罗西想了想说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿不会做衣服，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>再说她还有更重要的事情去做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我马上就回来。”罗西对朋友们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走到停车场的另一边，按下手表上的按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么事？布洛姆市长？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长看起来很着急。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有大麻烦了，火箭女孩儿。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得有人偷走了警察总局。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”罗西问。她以为自己听错了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您认为有人从警察总局偷走了东西？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是！”布洛姆市长大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是有人偷走了警察总局！整栋大楼不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等一下......那......那是机器人吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噢，不！火箭女孩儿，我......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西的手表关闭了，画面也随着消失。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长？”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长，您还在吗？”没有回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好了！”罗西咽了咽口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>